txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Jewelled sword sheaths from the Men and half-orcs in the areas around Echad Dúnann. Deliver the items to Tinúriel at Echad Dúnann.
'It is good to know that there are fewer defilers upon our lands. Thank you.'
'The enemies of the Free Peoples surround us. They are Men and half-orcs from the north and south. Fight them back and bring me their sheaths, and I shall see you rewarded.'
Elves of Rivendell Task: Jewelled Sword Sheaths
Tinúriel at Echad Dúnann has requested that a collection of jewelled sword sheaths be delivered to her.
Deliver the jewelled sword sheaths to Tinúriel at Echad Dúnann in Eregion
You have accepted a task to deliver jewelled sword sheaths from the Men and half-orcs found near Echad Dúnann to the Elf-maid Tinúriel. Tinúriel can be found in Echad Dúnann.
Wanted: Jewelled sword sheaths from the Men and half-orcs in the areas around Echad Dúnann.
